					p OutWellness ATX, an inclusive wellness center and gym for the LGBTQ+ community, needed a website revamp to increase lead generation and better represent their inclusive brand.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Process
					p 
						| I partnered with 
						= link_to "Chien Industries", "https://www.chienindustries.com/"
						| , who focused on refining the messaging and copy, while I led the site's redesign. I created the sitemap, wireframes, and user flows, then designed high-fidelity mockups in Figma and developed the site in WordPress. The experience was rebuilt to guide users clearly through services, reinforce inclusivity, and improve SEO and mobile performance.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Outcome
					p The new site delivers a welcoming, user-friendly experience that highlights OutWellness ATXâ€™s mission and offerings, while improving clarity, engagement, and lead-generation potential.
					hr.my-4
					.row
						.col-md-6
							h6 Client
							p OutWellness ATX
						.col-md-6
							h6 Year
							p 2024
					.row.mb-3
						.col-md-6
							h6 Services
							p Website Design, Wordpress Development
						.col-md-6
							h6 Technologies
							p Figma, Wordpress, HTML, PHP, CSS, JS, Elementor
					.row
						= link_to 'View Website <i class="fad fa-external-link-alt"></i>'.html_safe, 'https://outwellnessatx.com/', target: "_blank"
			.col-12.col-md-7
				div.pt-md-10
